changelog.release_notes:
- Added possibility to show humidity;
- Added possibility to hide leading zero in hours;
- Optimized geolocation usage.

description:
Now weather will always make you smile.
Be pleasantly surprised by the new screen color every time weather was updated.

Always will notify you when bluetooth connection lost by vibration (except cases when watch is plugged to charge or DoNotDisturb mode turned on).
Battery status will always be shown on low charge.

- A lot of colors for screen background that updates randomly or set static color in the settings;
- Current weather of your location or any custom location you entered in the settings;
- Temperature in Fahrenheit or Celsius as you decide;
- Two weather servers: YahooWeather and OpenWeatherMap;
- Time in 12h or 24h format based on your watch's preference;
- Current date and day of week;
- Humidity;
- Hourly vibration;
- Do not disturb mode.

You can also setup to show always bluetooth status and battery charge if you want.

Just try. You'll like it!
